INSERT INTO recipes2 (id, aou_id, name, recipe) VALUES (575,0,'The Special Hidden Recipe of Leets Slippers','<font color=#FF0000> Ingredients </font><font color=#009B00>\n    - two leets\n	\n</font><font color=#FF0000> Recipe </font><font color=#FFFF00>\n    - First of all, you have to catch 2 leets. It`s easy, make a trap using a box, a wooden twig, a wire and a bronto burger. After some time hunting you will have your two leets.\n     - Next you have to turn the leet inside out to make sure the fur of the leet is inside. Easiest way to do this is simply to put your hand in the leet, but it`s needed to get inside him from the rear.\n    - To finish, grab the teeth of the leet and pull on them,  you have to pull in a quick movement in order to turn over the leet as a sock.\n    - Do the same with the next leet. There it is ! you have perfect Leet`s slippers ! hot, soft, ... that`s wonderful.\n\n</font><font color=#FF0000> Comments </font><font color=#009B00>\n    When your Leet`s slippers become cold, you can put them some seconds in the microwave.\n    After 5 times in the microwave, build another set as these will become smelly.');
