INSERT INTO recipes2 (id, aou_id, name, recipe) VALUES (583,0,'Drake Trials Quest','<font color=#FF0000> Foreword </font><font color=#009B00>\n    Find Drake Rodriguez in Jobe Backyard. ( You have to be below level 50 to enter Jobe backyard ). Drake will give you 5 little quests and a <img src=''rdb://227249''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 223762''>Bracer of Jobe</a>.\n\n</font><font color=#FF0000> Test of Strength </font><font color=#009B00>\n    You have to kill a Deceitful Weaver, a Shining Coiler and a Beit Gras in 30 minutes. Beit Gras will require you to be around level 3.\n    Reward : <img src=''rdb://84047''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 223771''>Bracer of Strength</a> \n    \n</font><font color=#FF0000> Test of Agility and Stamina </font><font color=#009B00>\n    You have to target a Hungry Predator, a Lurking Chimera and a Pond Dryad in 3 minutes !!! so be quick. Use bracer to return to Drake quickly. Note: if you pre-spot the critters you can target the 1st two from the bridge.\n    Reward : depending on you profession.\n    \n</font><font color=#FF0000> Test of Sense </font><font color=#009B00>\n    Drake ask you to find a shadowleet. you can find it by using the search icon on menu 2 ( CTRL+2) near the guards area.\n    Reward: <img src=''rdb://12259''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 223768''>Nano Crystal (Overview of Nascence)</a>    \n    \n</font><font color=#FF0000> Test of Psychic </font><font color=#009B00>\n  You must do 1 of these 2 quests.\n    Talk to Talk to Celeth-El (omni) or El-Domo(clan) \n    Reward: <img src=''rdb://84059''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 223769''>Ring of Enhanced Psychic</a> \nCeleth-El will also change your bracer to <img src=''rdb://227249''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 233804''>Scourged Bracer of Jobe</a> if you hand it over. Then you need to get another from Drake to continue the quests.\n    \n</font><font color=#FF0000> Test of Intelligence </font><font color=#009B00>\n    You have to deliver some supplies to Sarah Willis </font><font color=#FFFF00>(355.1x252.5)</font><font color=#009B00>. Sarah Willis is behind a big creature you can`t kill, so you have to distract it. For that, speak to Brad Willis ( a mixture between Brad Pit and Bruce Willis ... ) let him start fighting the creature while you run like heck to speak to Sarah. then return to Drake.\n    Reward: <img src=''rdb://205499''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 223773''>Bonfire Kit</a>\n    \n</font><font color=#FF0000> Final Test </font><font color=#009B00>\n    Find Heckler of Evolution, kill it and loot the <img src=''rdb://227248''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 223763''>Delicate Metal Device</a> from him. Go back to Drake and trade him the device.\n    Reward: <img src=''rdb://99661''> <a href=''chatcmd:///tell <myname> show me item 223770''>Smart Backpack</a>\n\n</font><font color=#009B00>-----------------------------------------------------\nOnline Link :\n- <a href=''chatcmd:///start http://arcanum.aodevs.com/quest_sl-drake.html''>http://arcanum.aodevs.com/quest_sl-drake.html</a>');
